value.title: Trump lawyer Bruce Castor plays a central role in Bill Cosby going free
value.excerpt: Castor's representation of Trump in his impeachment trial raised questions about his past decisions about Cosby's prosecution. Now the Pennsylvania Supreme Court has set Cosby free based upon Castor's testimony.

value.title: Durbin slams Biden admin for 'unacceptable' delays in handling DACA applications
